OL,7,FThe families of the victims of triple
OL,8,Fkiller Valdo Calocane have condemned
OL,9,Fpolice for "ongoing mismanagement" of
OL,10,Fthe case including the alleged
OL,11,Fmisconduct of officers involved.
OL,13,FNottinghamshire Police have come under
OL,14,Ffire from the relatives, who accused
OL,15,Fthe force of "ongoing mismanagement"
OL,16,Fas they continued to raise "serious
OL,17,Fconcerns" about the way police have
OL,18,Fhandled the case.
