OL,7,FThey also criticised the force for
OL,8,Fholding a non-reportable briefing with
OL,9,Fthe press last week, accusing of
OL,10,F"gagging" the media.
OL,12,FIt comes just a week after it was ,
OL,13,Fwhile 11 members of staff viewed
OL,14,Fmaterial relating to the case who did
OL,15,Fnot have a legitimate reason to do so.
OL,17,FThe constable's dismissal comes after
OL,18,FNottinghamshire Police has faced
OL,19,Fseparate criticism for multiple cases
OL,20,Fof misconduct.
