OL,7,FBarnaby and Grace, both 19, were
OL,8,Fwalking home from an end-of-term night
OL,9,Fout when they were stabbed repeatedly
OL,10,Fby Valdo Calocane in Ilkeston Road,
OL,11,FRadford, near their student
OL,12,Faccommodation.
OL,14,FValdo Caolcane then went on to attack
OL,15,Fcaretaker Ian Coates, before stealing
OL,16,Fhis van and crashing it into three
OL,17,Fpedestrians on June 13 2023.
