OL,7,FCalocane was sentenced to an
OL,8,Findefinite hospital order last month
OL,9,Ffor stabbing to death university
OL,10,Fstudents Barnaby Webber, 19, and Grace
OL,11,FO'Malley-Kumar, 19, and school
OL,12,Fcaretaker Ian Coates, 65, in the early
OL,13,Fhours of June 13 last year.
OL,15,FHe admitted manslaughter by diminished
OL,16,Fresponsibility and pleaded guilty to
OL,17,Fthe attempted murder of three people
OL,18,Fwho were hit by a van stolen from Mr
OL,19,FCoates, after Nottingham Crown Court
OL,20,Fheard he had been diagnosed with
OL,21,Fparanoid schizophrenia.
