OL,5,Ccase
OL,7,F"We understand that this is a lengthy
OL,8,Fand detailed statement, however feel
OL,9,Fthat it is of the utmost importance
OL,10,Fthat our serious concerns and ongoing
OL,11,Fmismanagement by the Nottingham Police
OL,12,Fare brought to light.
OL,14,F"We will not be silenced.
OL,16,F"This behaviour must be addressed and
OL,17,Furgent changes made as this must not
OL,18,Fhappen again to other innocent
OL,19,Ffamilies."
